com.epimorphics.lda.core

Class View

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epimorphics.lda.core.View

  • public class View
extends Object
    Represents a view which selects which parts of a result resource to show, defined by a (possibly) ordered list of properties.
    Version:
    $Revision: $
    Author:
    Dave Reynolds

      • minExpiryMillis

        public long minExpiryMillis(PropertyExpiryTimes pet,
                   long givenDuration)
        minExpiryTime(pet, dur) returns the minimum of the expiry times for predicates in this view. A predicate of propertySTAR, representing *, forces the result to use the smallest expiry time of any predicate. The result is the smaller of the givenDuration and the minimum expiry time.
